After digging the moment.js documentation found the solution for my issue,


    // Round relative time evaluation down
    moment.relativeTimeRounding(Math.floor);
    
    moment.relativeTimeThreshold(&#39;s&#39;, 60);
    moment.relativeTimeThreshold(&#39;m&#39;, 60);
    moment.relativeTimeThreshold(&#39;h&#39;, 24);
    moment.relativeTimeThreshold(&#39;d&#39;, 31);
    moment.relativeTimeThreshold(&#39;M&#39;, 12);


relativeTimeRounding - sets the rounding function.
relativeTimeThreshold - sets the cutoff/threshold value for seconds,minutues,hours,etc.

